title: Andy Roy
itunes:title: Andy Roy
description:
My HoneyDew this week is Andy Roy! Andy is a former professional skateboarder who talks about coming up through the ranks to become pro. Along the way he made some bad choices that lead to addiction, a life of crime, and ultimately prison. Andy shares stories about prison life, gnarly places to inject heroin and a desire to get his teeth knocked out in a fight. It’s a Dewzie!
